com.saggezza.jtracker.track

Interface PayloadMap

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    PayloadMapC

    public interface PayloadMap
    PayloadMap interface The PayloadMap is used to store all the parameters and configurations that are used to send data via the HTTP GET request. PayloadMaps have an immutable structure for secure and accurate transfers of information.
